Author: algorthin
Text: Yea. I read recently that anorexia is an impulse control disorder which... Looking at like, my #tendencies, I should have known but I didn't, and opposite action is seeming to be a lot more possible since I was like "oh."

Author: fatnewlife
Text: That's my trick for living well. What do I want to do? Do the complete opposite for good results!  I don't feel like having a shower. I don't feel like flossing. I don't want to go for a walk. I wanna eat some ben and jerrys. I wanna buy this bottle of vodka. I want to text my ex bf.  My life goes best when I do the opposite of what I want.
